text: Jamesburg is a borough in Middlesex County, New Jersey, United States. As of the 2020 United States Census, the borough's population was 5,783. ==Geography== According to the United States Census Bureau, the borough has a total area of 0.883 square miles (2.289 km2). ==References== Category:Boroughs in New Jersey Category:Middlesex County, New Jersey Category:1887 establishments in the United States Category:19th-century establishments in New Jersey
title: Jamesburg, New Jersey
